        wishes to engage counsel, should there be an appeal, only are to have
        access to the Business Case Report held by the Court.&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;note&gt;
    &lt;bodytext&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/bodytext&gt;
